---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import CautionBox from "../components/CautionBox.astro"
---

<Layout title="Paulina Castillo">

	<h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Presentation video</h2>
	<!-- Poner el aviso de poner subtitulos -->
	<CautionBox  > Please set the subtitles in English.</CautionBox>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 via-white to-cyan-50 shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 mt-5">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
      Reducing networks without losing their flow
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[1.05rem] text-gray-700">
      It began on daily carpool rides to the university. My classmates wanted the shortest walk, I wanted the fewest turns — and somewhere between their requests and my optimizations I started seeing nodes, edges, and constraints instead of streets. That small negotiation became the seed of my fascination with networks and efficiency. Years later it turned into a thesis that pushed me to personal and computational limits: full-time work, two graduate courses, and late-night reinforcement-learning runs until convergence. The result — networks reduced by almost half while preserving 95%+ of flow — reminded me that the algorithms I taught to adapt and endure mirrored my own journey. This project is more than research; it’s proof that resilience, like flow, finds its way through even the most complex networks.
    </p>

    <!-- Mini-metrics -->
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur px-4 py-3">
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Gas / Water / Power</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">60–70% arcs</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">kept</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur px-4 py-3">
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Flow preserved</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">95%+</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">under scenarios</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white/70 backdrop-blur px-4 py-3">
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Compute pushed</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">~90% CPU</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">batched MCFP + VPG</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Actions -->
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="#methodology" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-gray-900 text-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-800">
        See methodology
      </a>
      <a href="#results" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-white border px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50">
        View results & plots
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative network dots -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-16 -bottom-16 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-cyan-200/30 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-20 -top-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-indigo-200/30 blur-3xl"></div>
</section>

